<div class="offcanvas offcanvas-end" tabindex="-1" id="offcanvasFilters" aria-labelledby="offcanvasFiltersLabel">
    <div class="offcanvas-header">
        <h5 class="offcanvas-title" id="offcanvasFiltersLabel"><i class="ti ti-filter me-2"></i>Фильтры</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas" aria-label="Close"></button>
    </div>
    <div class="offcanvas-body">
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">Статус</label>
            <select class="form-select">
                <option>Все</option>
                <option>ОК</option>
                <option>Ожидает</option>
                <option>Риск</option>
            </select>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">Период</label>
            <div class="row g-2">
                <div class="col-6"><input class="form-control" placeholder="с"></div>
                <div class="col-6"><input class="form-control" placeholder="по"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
            <button class="btn btn-primary w-100">Применить</button>
            <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary w-100" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas">Закрыть</button>
        </div>
        <div class="text-muted mt-3">Паттерн: фильтры/настройки — в offcanvas, чтобы не утяжелять страницу.</div>
    </div>
</div>
